00:11:11.210 --> 00:11:13.400
L'eau est l'élément principal de nos corps.

00:11:13.570 --> 00:11:15.920
Caoutchouc ou pas, ça ne change rien !

00:11:26.610 --> 00:11:28.320
Tu l'auras cherché !

00:11:31.970 --> 00:11:34.040
Tu ne passeras pas, luffy !

00:11:35.570 --> 00:11:36.760
Gear second.

00:11:37.290 --> 00:11:38.800
Gumgum...

00:11:39.770 --> 00:11:42.520
Jet stamp !

00:11:50.450 --> 00:11:52.760
C'est tout ce que ça donne, ton entraînement ?

00:11:53.850 --> 00:11:54.960
